      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with plates to ensure structural integrity. Power is delivered to the asphalt via a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis remains taut with original bushings and a perfectly preserved suspension geometry. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this M3 boasts original VIN-matching panels and a showroom-level finish. A true driver\u2019s car with zero deferred maintenance.",
