      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no creasing or bolster wear, and the factory scent remains present. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the multi-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history exclusively from authorized dealerships and a pristine engine bay that reflects its low-mileage, pampered life. This is a turnkey, collector-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who demands perfection. Sale includes all original keys, factory manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
